specify the IP addresses or hostnames of the nodes below separated by ',' as shown below.
NODES_IP_ADDRS="192.168.1.22,192.168.1.65"

specify the glusterfs version belowlike shown
GLUSTER_TARBALL="glusterfs-3.3.0qa14.tar.gz"

specify the directory structure in each machine where glusterfs tarball will be untarred and installed.
NODE_BUILD_DIR="/home/hadoop/Gluster"

username and password of machines. It is assumed that each machine has same username and password.
USERNAME="root"
PASSWORD="xxxx"
